Name: Time Loop Fighter
About the game: A simple SHMUP inspired by arcade classics of the 80s for quick but challenging fun! Jump through the 5 different time zones, blast your way out and catch all bonuses you can! Are you brave enough to beat that highscore? Game features: - 5 Different Time Zones - 5 Unique Boss Encounters - Online Leaderboard - Endless Game - Infinite Score And Fun!
